'''
Write a program to calculate the electricity bill (accept number of unit from user)
according to the following criteria:
> Unit Price First 100 units no charge
> Next 100 units ₹5 per unit
> After 200 units ₹10 per unit
'''

units = int(input("Enter number of units consumed: "))

if units <= 100:
    bill = 0
elif units <= 200:
    bill = (units - 100) * 5
else:
    bill = (100 * 5) + (units - 200) * 10

print("Electricity bill is: ₹", bill)

# OUTPUT 
'''
Enter number of units consumed: 80
Electricity bill is: ₹ 0

Enter number of units consumed: 150
Electricity bill is: ₹ 250

Enter number of units consumed: 250
Electricity bill is: ₹ 1000
'''
